Package: nucdataBaynet
Type: Package
Title: Nuclear Data Evaluation Using a Bayesian Network
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Georg Schnabel [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Georg Schnabel <georg.schnabel@nucleardata.com>
Description: This package enables the modelisation of statistical
    and systematic experimental errors, model defects, and
    parameter uncertainties as multivariate normal distributions.
    It provides functions for inference on the values of parameters
    and errors treating the system as a Bayesian network.
License: GPL (>= 3) 
URL: https://www.r-project.org, https://github.com/gschnabel/nucdataBaynet
BugReports: https://github.com/gschnabel/nucdataBaynet/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
Imports: data.table,
         Matrix
